
0.4.4 (19-07-2004)
	* setting default encoding to utf-8
	* whrandom replaced by random
	* function for input IPv4 addresses - ip("192.168.0.1")
	* set of swap functions added (swap16, swap16l, swap16h, swap32)

0.4.2 (05-02-2004)
	* gtk-2 version

0.2.2 (29-04-2003)
	* config dir creation fix. (Thanks to Kristoffer Erlandsson)

0.2.1 (23-03-2003)
	* added commandline '-m' option to disable menu, some minor
	  gui changes. New bits() function and configurable binary 
	  separators were added.

0.2.0 (03-05-2002)
	* preferences dialog, new functions and gui improvements.

0.1.10 (22-02-2002)
	* win32 fixes (Thanks to Frank Jacques), small changes,
	  two new configuration options.

0.1.9 (12-02-2002)
	* small gui changes, more configuration options, manual page,
	  online functions list.

0.1.8 (27-01-2002)
	* first public release.

